## Scoring-Matrix

### Beispiel: Zielgruppe = Abnehmwillige, Ziel = Leadgenerierung

```json
{
  "target_group": "Abnehmwillige",
  "goal": "lead",
  "scoring": {
    "cta_score": 10,
    "trust_score": 8,
    "price_score": 3,
    "seo_score": 9,
    "mobile_score": 9
  }
}
```

